<i>noun</i>: 카펫 [], 융단 [융단], 깔개 [깔개] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>카펫 []</dt><br>
<dd>carpet; rug</dd><br>
<dd>양털 등의 털로 겉면에 보푸라기가 일게 짠 두꺼운 모직물.</dd><br>
<dd>A thick mat woven with wool, etc., whose surface is nappy.</dd><br>
<dt>융단 [융단]</dt><br>
<dd>carpet; rug</dd><br>
<dd>양털 등의 털을 겉에 보풀이 일게 짠 두꺼운 천.</dd><br>
<dd>A thick cloth woven with fur such as wool, whose surface is nappy.</dd><br>
<dt>깔개 [깔개]</dt><br>
<dd>mat; rug</dd><br>
<dd>앉거나 눕기 위해 바닥에 까는 얇고 넓적한 물건.</dd><br>
<dd>A thin, large object spread on the floor so that one can sit or lie on it.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>